Token.Abstract: a AWSServiceConfiguration object contains credentialsProvider and endpoint instance. credentialProvider contains accessKey, secretKey, and maybe sessionKey if STS credential is used. endpoint contains regionType and serviceType. If endpoint is nil, AWSRegionUSEast1 and AWSServiceS3 will be used as default value.
Build a time-limited pre-signed URL to get object from S3, return nil if build process failed.

Parameter.Name: preSignedURLRequest
Parameter.Abstract: The AWSS3PreSignedURLRequest that defines the parameters of the operation.

ReturnValue.Abstract: A pre-signed NSURL for the resource. return nil if any errors occured.
